3"},"133:46–53"],". What do these passages teach about the Savior’s Second Coming?"]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para","The Savior’s Second Coming will usher in the thousand-year period called the Millennium. What will life on earth be like during the Millennium? (See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.58-59"},"D&C 45:58–59"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.23-34"},"101:23–34"],".) How can this knowledge about the Millennium be a blessing in your life now?"]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para","What can you do in your life now to prepare for the Second Coming? (See the scripture chain below.)"]]],[".topic",["h2","Scripture Chain: Preparing for the Second Coming"],["ul.noMarker",["li",[".para",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.15-18"},"D&C 27:15–18"]]],["li",[".para",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.20-23"},"D&C 43:20–23"]]],["li",[".para",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.32,35,56-57"},"D&C 45:32, 35, 56–57"]]],["li",[".para",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.22-23"},"D&C 101:22–23"]]],["li",[".para",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.4-5,11"},"D&C 133:4–5, 11"]]]]]]],"refs":null}
